Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity

Class LogEntity

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity.LogEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class LogEntity extends Object implements Serializable
The LogEntity class represents the "log" table in the database. Each instance of this class corresponds to a single row in the table.
